Attention Dear Beneficiary Mrs. Eve

You have been compensated with the sum of  $ 3.5 million dollars in this
Nation Intergovernmental Organization, United Nations Office for Project
Services. The payment will be issued into your bank account in the Bank Of
Africa (B.O.A). So for that reason, We need the below requirement from you
in order for us to direct you to the paying bank.


(1)  Your Full Name:

(2)  Your Country:

(3)  Your Resident Address:

(4)  Your Occupation:

(5)  Your Call No:

(6)  Your Passport:


thanks,
Mrs. bill chantal
Regional Operations Senior Officer United Nation Intergovernmental
Organization
